&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;also clean up the internal `RecordDeserializer` state during cleanup of input channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


